'''SCS Software s.r.o.''' 是[[捷克|捷克]][[布拉格|布拉格]]的一間[[电子游戏|電子游戏]][[游戏开发者|开发公司]]，主要開發[[Microsoft|微軟]][[Windows|Windows]]，[[MacOS|MacOS]]和[[Linux|Linux]]的運輸[[模擬遊戲|模拟游戏]]，包括{{link-en|18輪鋼|18 Wheels of Steel}}系列和卡车模拟系列。

== 遊戲 ==

=== 巴士駕駛員 ===

SCS在2007年发布了一个巴士駕駛模拟游戏《[[巴士駕駛員|巴士駕駛員]]》。<ref name="IGN-pr">{{cite press release|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/06/04/bus-driver-is-running-on-time|title=Bus Driver is Running 'On-Time'|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=4 June 2008|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101101025/https://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/06/04/bus-driver-is-running-on-time|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2014年，iOS版推出，名為“巴士駕駛員 - Pocket Edition”。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/211923/MERIDIAN4_BRINGS_FANLOVED_PC_SIM_BUS_DRIVER_TO_iOS.php|title=Meridian4 Brings Fan-Loved PC Sim ''Bus Driver'' to iOS|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date=27 February 2014|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220850/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/211923/MERIDIAN4_BRINGS_FANLOVED_PC_SIM_BUS_DRIVER_TO_iOS.php|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===18輪鋼===

《{{link-en|18輪鋼|18 Wheels of Steel}}》系列主要集中在[[北美地区|北美地区]]。 该系列由Valusoft出版，从2002年《Hard Truck: 18 Wheels of Steel》推出起，直到2011年的《18 Wheels of Steel: Extreme Trucker 2》。

=== 卡车模拟系列 ===

卡车模拟系列包括2008年推出的《[[歐洲卡車模擬|歐洲卡車模擬]]》、2012年推出的续集《[[歐洲卡車模擬2|歐洲卡車模擬2]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.twinfinite.net/2014/12/30/crew-fails-euro-truck-simulator-2-succeeds/2/|title=Why The Crew Fails Where Euro Truck Simulator 2 Succeeds|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=30 December 2014|last=Fox|first=Chris|publisher=Twinfinite.net|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017081856/http://www.twinfinite.net/2014/12/30/crew-fails-euro-truck-simulator-2-succeeds/2|archive-date=2015-10-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和2016年推出的《[[美洲卡車模擬|美洲卡車模擬]]》。 系列集中在一系列欧洲国家，例如[[英国|英国]]、[[德国|德国]]、[[捷克|捷克]]、[[卢森堡|卢森堡]]、[[意大利|意大利]]、[[法国|法国]]、[[比利时|比利时]]、[[荷兰|荷兰]]、[[奥地利|奥地利]]和[[瑞士|瑞士]]<ref name="vice">{{cite web|url=http://www.vice.com/read/i-played-a-truck-simulator-for-30-hours-389|title=I Played a Truck Simulator Video Game for 30 Hours and Have Never Felt More at Peace|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=22 January 2015|last=Kelly|first=Andy|work=[[Vice_(magazine)|Vice]]|archive-date=2016-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161205134339/http://www.vice.com/read/i-played-a-truck-simulator-for-30-hours-389|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/feature/a562137/6-weird-simulator-games-from-london-underground-to-street-cleaning.html|title=6 weird Simulator games: From London Underground to street cleaning|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=4 April 2014|last=Lee|first=Ben|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022101142/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/feature/a562137/6-weird-simulator-games-from-london-underground-to-street-cleaning.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="idigitaltimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.idigitaltimes.com/euro-truck-simulator-2-scandinavia-dlc-release-date-teaser-trailer-and-screenshots-430699|title=Euro Truck Simulator 2: Scandinavia DLC Release Date, Teaser Trailer And Screenshots Released By SCS|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=7 April 2015|last=Craft|first=Scott|publisher=IDigitalTimes.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409072702/http://www.idigitaltimes.com/euro-truck-simulator-2-scandinavia-dlc-release-date-teaser-trailer-and-screenshots-430699|archivedate=2015年4月9日}}</ref>以及美國駕駛卡车。

SCS還发布了许多的的地图作为欧洲的卡车模拟2的[[追加下载内容|追加下载内容]] (DLC) 。第一个《Going East!》在2013年底发布，包括一些[[东欧|东欧]]国家，加入了[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]、[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]和[[波兰|波兰]]等更多城市<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/euro-truck-simulator-2-heads-east-for-its-first-dlc-expansion/|title=Euro Truck Simulator 2 heads east for its first DLC expansion|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=4 September 2013|last=Savage|first=Phil|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608150516/http://www.pcgamer.com//euro-truck-simulator-2-heads-east-for-its-first-dlc-expansion/|archive-date=2017-06-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="pcgamer-Scand">{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/euro-truck-simulator-2-screenshots-show-upcoming-scandinavia-dlc/|title=Euro Truck Simulator 2 screenshots show upcoming Scandinavia DLC|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=9 January 2015|last=Savage|first=Phil|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608135647/http://www.pcgamer.com/euro-truck-simulator-2-screenshots-show-upcoming-scandinavia-dlc/|archive-date=2017-06-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；第二个《Scandinavia》在2015年发布，加入了[[北歐|北歐]][[斯堪的纳维亚|斯堪的纳维亚]]地區，包括[[丹麦|丹麦]]、[[挪威|挪威]]和[[瑞典|瑞典]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/04/05/euro-truck-simulator-2-scandinavia-gets-release-date-teaser/143030/|title=Euro Truck Simulator 2 – Scandinavia Gets Release Date, Teaser|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=5 April 2015|last=Zutter|first=Ben|work=Hardcore Gamer|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230002/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/04/05/euro-truck-simulator-2-scandinavia-gets-release-date-teaser/143030/|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；第三个《Viva la France》在2016年底发布，加入了法国的更多城市。其他更新，包括[[梅赛德斯-奔驰|賓士]]卡車的商标和品牌的使用授权。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.technopat.net/2015/03/26/mercedes-sonunda-ets-2ye-resmen-geliyor/|title=Mercedes Sonunda ETS 2'ye Resmen Geliyor|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=26 March 2015|last=Güngör|first=Berker|publisher=Technopat|language=tr|trans-title=Mercedes finally officially coming to ETS 2|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305050715/https://www.technopat.net/2015/03/26/mercedes-sonunda-ets-2ye-resmen-geliyor/|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

緊隨欧洲卡车模拟2的成功，SCS宣布，系列中下一个游戏会是《美洲卡车模拟》，並在2016年2月3日发布。 然而，游戏早了一天在2016年2月2日发布。 游戏獲得正式授权的卡車品牌包括Peterbilt、Kenworth、[[沃尔沃集团|沃尔沃]]、{{le|國際孤星|International LoneStar}}和[[麥克貨車|麥克貨車]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/05/06/road-to-joy-american-truck-simulator-images/|title=Road To Joy: American Truck Simulator Images|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=6 May 2014|last=Smith|first=Adam|work=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729054104/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/05/06/road-to-joy-american-truck-simulator-images/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.incgamers.com/2014/04/american-truck-simulator-images-release-date-info|title=American Truck Simulator images and "moving target" release date info|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=13 April 2014|last=Parrish|first=Peter|publisher=IncGamers|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510160618/http://www.incgamers.com/2014/04/american-truck-simulator-images-release-date-info|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://gamingbolt.com/american-truck-simulator-wiki|title=American Truck Simulator Wiki – Everything you need to know about the game|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=16 December 2014|last=Toney|first=Martin|publisher=Gamingbolt.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422205415/http://gamingbolt.com/american-truck-simulator-wiki|archive-date=2017-04-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/american-truck-simulator-devs-release-an-hour-of-alpha-footage/|title=American Truck Simulator devs release an hour of alpha footage|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=27 January 2015|last=Savage|first=Phil|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170604035101/http://www.pcgamer.com//american-truck-simulator-devs-release-an-hour-of-alpha-footage/|archive-date=2017-06-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>游戏隨[[加州|加州]]和[[内华达州|内华达州]]推出；2016年6月，[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]作为一个免费的DLC发布。 大多数未来的州份地图将收費。

